com.twitter.sdk.android.tweetui

Interface Timeline<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - timeline item type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CollectionTimeline, FixedTweetTimeline, SearchTimeline, TwitterListTimeline, UserTimeline

    public interface Timeline<T>
    Abstracts a source of items which are bi-directionally traversable (next and previous).

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void next(Long minPosition, <any> cb)
      Loads items with position greater than (above) minPosition.
      void previous(Long maxPosition, <any> cb)
      Loads items with position less than (below) maxId.

    • Method Detail

      • next

        void next(Long minPosition,
          <any> cb)
        Loads items with position greater than (above) minPosition. If minPosition is null, loads the newest items.
        Parameters:
        minPosition - minimum position of the items to load (exclusive).
        cb - callback.

      • previous

        void previous(Long maxPosition,
              <any> cb)
        Loads items with position less than (below) maxId.
        Parameters:
        maxPosition - maximum position of the items to load (exclusive).
        cb - callback.
